      "rationale": "All three FEA codes (FDA in-house, Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1, DePuy Synthes proprietary solver) operate under documented QMS conforming to ISO 9001. Version control, change logs, and regression test suites are maintained. SQA level 2 is commensurate with model risk level 3 and medium assurance target."
